PLEASE NOTE THAT TO PLAY THIS GAME THE FILE narrator.device SHOULD
EXIST IN YOUR DEVS: DIRECTORY OR IN THE DIRECTORY THAT THE EXECUTABLE
FILE IS !!!
IF YOU TRY TO RUN THIS GAME WITHOUT HAVING THE narrator.device YOUR
SYSTEM WILL PROBABLY CRASH!!!

ALSO KEEP THE FILE hi.dat WHICH KEEPS THE HISCORES IN THE SAME DIRECTORY
WITH THE EXECUTABLE


